coin,=E2=80=9D Elon Musk tweeted this morning. The price of Dogecoin prompt=
ly shot up by about 6%, before giving back about half of those gains, so he=
=E2=80=99s still got it I guess. McDonald=E2=80=99s stock was not open for =
trading at the time of his tweet, but it did open down from yesterday=E2=80=
=99s close; as of about 11 a.m., it was down about 1.7%. =E2=80=9CElon Musk=
 can still move memecoin prices by tweeting, but now he is powerless over=
=C2=A0household-name mega-cap public companies that are totally unrelated t=
o his business,=E2=80=9D is going to be my possibly overoptimistic conclusi=
on here.=C2=A0
