 It seems fairly straightforward, but there are some non-obvious elements. =
For instance, Points 1 and 2 are weird insofar as, in the U.S., <a href=3D"=
https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26482321.283628/aHR0cHM6Ly93d=
3cuaW52ZXN0b3IuZ292L2ludHJvZHVjdGlvbi1pbnZlc3RpbmcvaW52ZXN0aW5nLWJhc2ljcy9n=
